Package Class

Class Flight

java.lang.Object
Class.Flight
public class Flight extends Object
The Flight class is used in conjunction with information recollected from the API used in this project. All data concerning a flights will land in this class.
Since:
04/18/2023
Author:
Carlos Figueroa (developed class) and Ana Emily Castillo Perez (added documentation comments).

Explanation of important functions: Class implements user's flight choice when API lists relevant flights according to user's inputted flight characteristics.

Important data structure in class/important methods in class:

  • Flight(String flightID, Date departureDate, Date arrivalDate, Time departureTime, Time arrivalTime, String departureLocation, String arrivalLocation): used to store flight properties.

Any algorithms used? Not at the moment.
